title: What is life like in Košice?
itunes:author: The Slovak Spectator
itunes:summary:
Ingeborg Jørgensen and Sergei Batiashov reveal what their life in the capital of eastern Slovakia has been like in the last three years, what to do in Košice, and where to go. 
 
Presenter: Peter Dlhopolec
